{"type":"message","id":"da940e8a","parentId":"fdfa6ca7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:29:30.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the current cron session itself. There's no actual user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The session listed is just this cron job running. Let me check if there are any other sessions with user activity by looking at sessions other than this cron session.\n\nActually, the sessions_list returns this cron session as the only session. The `contextTokens` shows 46719 which means this session has been going on. But the question is whether there's an active user conversation.\n\nLooking at the session - it's the cron job session itself. There's no other session with a user message. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"b6a8ed698f571c9b5905870f2fc8892c5304d0e48e65e0a3b977a89251eb602d"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron会话，没有用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n\n正在搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态...\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l1wvk3aa60nn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":816,"output":224,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45021,"cost":{"input":0.0002448,"output":0.0002688,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018330299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104165403}}
